Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Time's Up!\N Red-Eyes Black Metal Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Their Life Points are pretty close,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Jounouchi-kun scored a lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can win, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better, for Shizuka-chan's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! You better stay at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The game has shifted to Jounouchi boy's favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Based on experience, deck strength and strategy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi boy is nowhere near close to Keith's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So then, what is making up for the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After Keith lost that Duel to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he became obsessed with alcohol and drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and fell into an untouchable world of the underground gambling unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look! This is the proof of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we're separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're always connected by this bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One side is driven by despair and revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While the other is lead by hope and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seeing both of their minds, this is almost a battle of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in the end, who will the Goddess of Victory smile on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's so funny, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kid, have you ever been pushed to the far edge of sanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point where you risk everything to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pushed to the far edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you've ever {\i1}seen{\i0} hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risking everything to save yourself, no matter what the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only escape from my hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is right through Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything I have to do to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means going to hell and back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so big and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you forgot something really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a shame, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't gonna reach Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz I'm gonna beat you right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's {\i1}your{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What blasphemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I play this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know what it feels like to gamble in {\i1}hell{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolver Dragon is equipped with three guns, each holding three bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have a 50/50 chance of survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50/50 chance...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolver Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gun Cannon Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters were wiped out...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of the Revolver Dragon Heads has 2600 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, the chambers will reload on my next turn, and it'll start over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can attack up to three times per turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a powerful card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in trouble, no matter how many Monsters he plays!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now ain't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll use this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight a gamble {\i1}with{\i0} a gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Time Magician...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is! Jounouchi's trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Time Roulette works, his Machine Monsters will all rust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops... That wasn't the only card I was gonna play on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your show time now, Baby Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Time Magician Combo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can transform into Thousand Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he'll blow a huge hole in your Machine Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Roulette!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this roulette fails, Jounouchi-kun's Monster will be wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he'll lose half its Attack Points out of his Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge gamble on luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's slowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Nose Breath!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I annihilated that Revolver Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That my Machine Cards are invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Machine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That capsule...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's opening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Attack and Defense went back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gun Cannon Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one of my Monsters gets killed in combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use this Trap Card, Time Machine, to call back the Monster from a previous turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with its original Attack and Defense Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster from one turn back...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as he killed the Revolver Dragon, a new undamaged one from the previous turn appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Jounouchi-kun's trump card combo was beaten this easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keith really is a powerful opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I memorized that pathetic deck of yours back when you fought against Kotsuzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's just the worthless deck of an amateur with no true strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he read right through my plan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get another Monster out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show you just how worthless your cards are against my ultimate deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster in Defense Mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you're gonna do, I'll also play another...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monster in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then take out your Defense Monster with Revolver Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, ya weaklin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still have the Red-Eyes in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I use it to attack that machine of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Revolver Dragon will just wipe it out next turn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I really play Red-Eyes that easily...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a way to turn this around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes Black Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card may be the strongest card in your deck with the highest Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it ain't no match against my Revolver Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, I'll be glad to take it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolver Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, The card I set earlier was the Mimic Illusionist card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy can copy any one of your cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card I'm copying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Metal Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes Black Metal Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the copy card, he came back from the brinks of defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Mega Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolver Dragon is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandit Keith!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you think it's just luck or a miracle that I'm beating you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could care less either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I win, I can save Shizuka's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I strongly believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better enjoy your gloating while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a ton of different ways to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that a worthless amateur's no-strategy deck
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't stand a chance against a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to victory is the difference in our skill level!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Difference in our skill level", heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your Life's been falling lower than mine~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bullshit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}my{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One card face-down on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slot Machine goes to Defense Mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my turn's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Machine Monster only has 2300 Defense Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Red-Eyes can take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Slot Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Mega Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll use this face-down card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7 Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number seven just appeared on the Slot Machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card is a power unit that increases the Slot Machine's Defense Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It raises Slot Machine's Defense Power by 700 points, up to 3000!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Red-Eyes' attack won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack bounced back, and my Life Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he can't lay a hand on the Slot Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slot Machine's Attack or Defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can choose to power up either one with the 7 Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a total of 2100 points in damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna show you the true difference in our skill level.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use another 7 Card this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this to raise its Attack Power by 700 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This asshole...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's just gonna keep on increasing its Attack Power while it's in Defense Mode...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he uses one more of those 7 Cards on the Slot Machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll have 3400 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Red-Eyes stands no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna play another card as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sphere Bomb!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a time bomb, set to go off on your next turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that'll inflict 2900 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this thing self-destructs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red-Eyes will be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up, kid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IDIOT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the frig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing really saved me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dark Claws of the Dragon-Types"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Equipment Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Attack goes up by 600 points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes to make people worry about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe {\i1}my{\i0} Life gets slashed {\i1}instead{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This damn {\b0}brat{\b1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In {\i1}that{\i0} case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use another 7 Card on my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring up its Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Monsters have the same Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And both Jounouchi and Keith have practically the same amount of Life Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match will be decided this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a card in my hand that could turn the tables...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I use that now, it'll only further my disadvantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ain't gonna make a move, I'll take my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, I {\i1}praise{\i0} you for makin' it this far against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bandit card allows me to look at the opponent's hand and take any card I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now which one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shield and Sword, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now ain't {\i1}this{\i0} a nice card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be takin' it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for ya, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shield in the Right Hand, Sword in the Left Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slot Machine goes to Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plasma Laser Cannon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set Card, open!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wi-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Graverobber card...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no {\b0}way{\b1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He {\b0}stole{\b1} the Time Machine card from my Graveyard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly proud of beating you by stealing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time Machine card can bring back a Monster from the previous turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning one turn back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The offense and defensive switch didn't happen yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Red-Eyes Black Metal Dragon revives at full strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat {\i1}this{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Mega Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As great as I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to that {\i1}kid{\i0}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this battle of hope and despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Goddess of Victory has smiled on the side of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi-kun!\N-Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the winner is... Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I DID IT~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it, Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really did it, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel is invalid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to how low you can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entry card he showed wasn't even {\i1}his{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't even permitted to participate in this Duel from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find my card anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mai gave me her card in its place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the heck did you know this wasn't my card in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How the hell'd you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandit Keith...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole Jounouchi boy's card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you're the unforgivable one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I personally could care less {\i1}whose{\i0} card it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I {\i1}can't{\i0} forgive is you cheating during the Duel just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cheated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keith...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You added the 7 Card you kept hidden in your wristband to your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, no one can fool {\i1}my{\i0} eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keith, you lousy scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you shall be ejected from the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an excellent Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PEGASUS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure {\i1}are{\i0} a persistent one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over the prize money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I'll take your life right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see the once renowned "Prize King" like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have clearly lost the mind necessary for a Duelist,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I witnessed first hand in the match just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you bullshit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell's the prize money!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like the small fry to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, excusing the interruption that just occurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we shall now begin the final round of the tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...featuring Yugi Mutou versus Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the time has finally come...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time for me and Jounouchi-kun to fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(136,148)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Jounouchi made it to the final round!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the two have to fight each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they best friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, just leave it to Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because{\i0} you're best friends, you'll fight at your best?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Final Game of Friendship! Yugi VS Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:21:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:22:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
